      .busines-preview__nav-item 
        input(type="radio" name="busines_preview" id="busines_preview_01" checked)
        label(for="busines_preview_01") Стартовый
      .busines-preview__nav-item 
        input(type="radio" name="busines_preview" id="busines_preview_02")
        label(for="busines_preview_02") Простой
